tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE commuter_traffic (
  station_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  station_name STRING,
  entrance_count INT,
  exit_count INT,
  peak_hour_traffic INT
);

CREATE TABLE station_usage (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    station_name VARCHAR(50),
    date DATE,
    time TIME,
    entry_count INT,
    exit_count INT
);

CREATE TABLE trips (
    trip_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    commuter_id UUID REFERENCES commuters (commuter_id),
    station_id UUID REFERENCES stations (station_id),
    trip_date DATE,
    trip_time TIME
);

CREATE TABLE traffic_reports (
    report_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    station_id INT,
    report_date DATE,
    total_entries INT,
    total_exits INT
);

CREATE TABLE station_activity (
    activity_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    station_id INT,
    activity_date DATE,
    total_entries INT,
    total_exits INT
);

CREATE TABLE Commuter_Schedules (
    schedule_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    train_id INT,
    station_id INT,
    arrival_time TIME,
    departure_time TIME,
    FOREIGN KEY (train_id) REFERENCES Commuter_Trains(train_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (station_id) REFERENCES Commuter_Stations(station_id)
);

CREATE TABLE Commuter_Traffic (
    traffic_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    station_id INT,
    traffic_count INT,
    date DATE,
    FOREIGN KEY (station_id) REFERENCES Commuter_Stations(station_id)
);
